text: You've got this!
It's supposed to be hard.
You can do it!
You can totally do this.
Impossible is for the unwilling.
No pressure, no diamonds.
Try Again. Fail again. Fail better.
I can and I will.
Prove them wrong.
Screw it, let’s do it.
Keep going. Be all in.
If you want it, work for it.
You can if you think you can.
Grow through what you go through.
Do it with passion or not at all.
The past does not equal the future.
At the end of hardship comes happiness.
Don’t dream your life, live your dream.
If it matters to you, you’ll find a way.
Whatever you do, do with all your might.
Every noble work is at first impossible.
If you’re going through hell, keep going.
Open your mind. Get up off the couch. Move.
Be faithful to that which exists within yourself.
Persistence guarantees that results are inevitable.
In life you need either inspiration or desperation.
The true success is the person who invented himself.
Go forth on your path, as it exists only through your walking.
We can do anything we want to if we stick to it long enough.
It is better to live one day as a lion, than a thousand days as a lamb.
Life is fragile. We’re not guaranteed a tomorrow so give it everything you’ve got.
Fall seven times, stand up eight.
Actually, you can.
Yes! Yes! You can do it!
You are amazing. Remember that.
You are capable of amazing things.
You are stronger than you think you are.
Focus on the journey, not the destination.
Believe you can and you’re halfway there.
Once you choose hope, anything’s possible.
You make mistakes. Mistakes don’t make you.
Start every day off with a smile and get it over with.
It’s okay to not be okay as long as you are not giving up.
If you feel like giving up, look back at how far you’ve come.
Every day may not be good but there is something good in every day.
Don’t go through life, grow through life.
Keep going.
No pain, no gain.
Keep your chin up.
Now is all you have.
Keep moving forward.
This too shall pass.
Every moment matters.
Dust settles. I don’t.
Nothing lasts forever.
Work hard. Stay humble.
Better things are coming.
The best is yet to come.
Whatever you do, do it well.
All limitations are self-imposed.
Tough times never last but tough people do.
One day the people that don’t even believe in you will tell everyone how they met you.
Have enough courage to start and enough heart to finish.
Determine your priorities and focus on them.
Be so good they can’t ignore you.
Yesterday you said tomorrow. Just do it.
I don’t need it to be easy, I need it to be worth it.
Never let your emotions overpower your intelligence.
There is no substitute for hard work.
Strive for greatness.
And still, I rise.
May your choices reflect your hopes, not your fears.
Turn your wounds into wisdom.
It hurt because it mattered.
I have nothing to lose but something to gain.
